    • Class minesweeper.logic.GameGrid extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • tiles

          Tile[][] tiles
          The actual game grid. A square array of tiles

        • started

          boolean started
          Indicates if the game has been started. I.e. if the tile array has been populated.

        • mines

          int mines
          Number of mines specified by the constructor. Note: May be higher than the actual number of mines in the array.

        • max

          Coordinate max
          Coordinate of the bottom right tile in the array. Usefull for tile validation.

        • gameType

          GameType gameType
          The type of game used for creating this grid.
